reviews.name: Miabella 1-1/4 Carat T.G.W. Cushion-Cut Created White Sapphire and Diamond Accent Sterling Silver Engagement Ring
reviews.reviewText: The pictures online do this ring no justice it is gorgeous everyone that sees it raves about it. They think it costed hundreds of dollars. I love it!
reviews.title: Great choice!

reviews.name: Miabella 1-1/4 Carat T.G.W. Cushion-Cut Created White Sapphire and Diamond Accent Sterling Silver Engagement Ring
reviews.reviewText:
I purchased this for my 19 year old daughters birthday. Its really cute and looks like a diamond. I have a white sapphire ring myself that is much
larger that she always wanted to wear. When I saw this, the price and size was just right for her. She loves this ring.
reviews.title: cute product for my daughters birthday

reviews.name: Miabella 1-1/4 Carat T.G.W. Cushion-Cut Created White Sapphire and Diamond Accent Sterling Silver Engagement Ring
reviews.reviewText:
I love this ring. I bought a different ring for about the same price (different brand) but it looked very cheap, I returned it. Then I ordered this ring hoping it wouldn't look the same as the other one. When i opened the box i was shocked. This ring is beautiful and the quality was way much better than the other one. This is a very nice ring, it looks expensive and nice.

I'm very pleased for what I paid, very nice. :)
reviews.title: nice ring for the price

reviews.name: Miabella 1-1/4 Carat T.G.W. Cushion-Cut Created White Sapphire and Diamond Accent Sterling Silver Engagement Ring
reviews.reviewText: I've purchased different brands of rings, but going off of other reviews I've always found them helpful and absolutely accurate. We beat up our rings pretty bad at work and they still last for quite some time. This product in particular was great for the price. My orders through walmart online have been 100% accurate and timely. Thank you walmart for always coming through!
reviews.title: Love purchasing walmart rings, who knew!

reviews.name: Miabella 1-1/4 Carat T.G.W. Cushion-Cut Created White Sapphire and Diamond Accent Sterling Silver Engagement Ring
reviews.reviewText: When my husband and I were first starting out we couldn't afford an engagement ring. Now with a fiery toddler running about and the cost of child care, a diamond seems like a ridiculous investment when our money is put to better use on things to make his and our life easier. When we saw this ring we thought, its beautiful! and the price makes it twice as nice. We bought it, hoping that when it arrived it would be as beautiful in person as it was online. It came a couple days ago and is even prettier in person! I get compliments on it every where I go!
reviews.title: even more beautiful in person!
